## 🚀 Quick start

**This repository is for checking the React code for the Full Stack Developer challenge.**

**To run the application go to the Server repository**

# Pre-requisites
- Install [Node.js]v15.0.0

# Getting stated
- Clone the respository
```

git clone https://github.com/ojmarte/Front-end-SweatWorks---Assignment-for-the-Full-Stack-Developer-position.git
```

- install dependencies
```

cd Front-end-SweatWorks---Assignment-for-the-Full-Stack-Developer-position/
npm install
```
- Buil and run the project
```
npm start
```

Navigate to `http://localhost:8000`
